Operating Procedures
1. Adding WalmartHunt to your Chrome browser
2. Viewing the Walmart products catalog or searching any keywords 
3. Now, you could evaluate product opportunities

-Q：How does WalmartHunt Chrome extension operated?
-A：Simple and easy to operate embedded interface - synchronously capture and calculate data when browsing Walmart Product List page, with a delay of < 1s.

Hope WalmartHunt makes your Walmart product research quicker and easier.
